[#expr.mul]
[para:change]
[:en] Specify rounding for results of integer [`/] and [`%]
[para:rationale]
[:en] Increase portability, C99 compatibility.
[para:effect]
[:en] Valid [=Cpp] 2003 code that uses integer division rounds the result toward
0 or toward negative infinity, whereas this International Standard always rounds
the result toward 0.
